io","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=3840&h=2160&q=80&fm=webp 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/7CmSVpPnKSAx3F7ExszWyg/9d5512dfacacd9367f07e5283af1ea3e/ko_-_portfolio.png?w=3840&h=2160&q=80&fm=png 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"July 17, 2023","authors":[{"name":"MetaMask","createProfilePage":null,"profileUrl":"metamask"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p><a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">MetaMask Portfolio</a>는 웹3의 모든 것을 위한 원스톱 쇼핑입니다. 여러 거래소, 디앱(DApp), 도구에 연결하는 대신 <a href=\"https://metamask.io/portfolio/?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">하나의 간편한 디앱</a>에 연결하기만 하면 모든 웹3의 필요를 충족할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>MetaMask Portfolio에서는 다음과 같은 기능으로 일반적인 업무를 간편하게 수행할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>대시보드</li>\n<li>매수</li>\n<li>스왑</li>\n<li>브릿지</li>\n<li>스테이크</li>\n</ul>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vGH6PoVaIS8\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<br /> \n<h4>대시보드: 한 곳에서 모든 것을 추적</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio를 처음 방문하시면 [모든 자산과 활동을 하나의 창에 모두 표시한] 대시보드를 만날 수 있습니다.(<a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/dashboard-track-everything-in-one-place/\">https://metamask.io/news/latest/dashboard-track-everything-in-one-place/</a>) 여기에 MetaMask 지갑의 주소를 붙여 넣어 지갑을 연결하고 확인할 수 있습니다. 대시보드는 여러 계정과 네트워크(이더리움, Optimism, 아비트럼, Polygon, 아발란체, Fantom, BNB 체인) 전반에서 포트폴리오를 집계하여 지갑이 보유하고 있는 자산에 대한 인사이트를 제공합니다. 잔고 계산과 온체인(On-Chain) 활동 추적을 위해 여러 디앱을 일일이 확인하는 대신, 한 곳에서 모든 것을 확인할 수 있습니다. NFT와 POAP도 대시보드에 표시됩니다!</p>\n<h4>매수: 간편하게 지갑에 자금 조달</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio의 \"매수\" 기능은 다양한 요소를 고려하여 지역, 결제 수단, 토큰, 금액에 따라 경쟁력 있는 견적을 제시하는 애그리게이터를 활용하여 <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/buy-fund-your-wallet-easily/\">암호화폐 구매를 간편하게 만들고 맞춤화합니다</a>. MetaMask는 결제 서비스 제공업체를 심사하여 안전한 거래를 지원합니다. 암호화폐 누구나 쉽게 구매할 수 있어야 합니다. MetaMask는 이 기능에 매료된 전 세계 신규 사용자의 유입에 자부심을 느낍니다.</p>\n<h3>매도: 암호화폐를 법정 화폐로 현금화</h3>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio의 \"매도\" 기능으로 사용자는 몇 번의 클릭만으로 검증된 제공업체를 통해 <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/how-to-use-metamasks-sell-feature-to-cash-out-your-crypto-to-fiat/\">암호화폐를 법정 화폐로 바꿀 수 있습니다</a>. MetaMask Portfolio의 매수 및 매도 기능을 사용하여 사용자는 동일한 공급업체를 통해 암호화폐에서 법정 화폐까지 모든 과정을 완벽하게 마무리할 수 있습니다. 이 과정에서 사용자는 특정 제공업체에 가입하고 은행 계좌를 한 번만 연결하면 됩니다.</p>\n<h4>스왑: 원하는 것 얻기</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio의 \"스왑\" 기능으로 사용자는 <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/swap-get-what-you-want/\">하나의 토큰을 다른 것으로 교환할 수 있습니다</a>. 다양한 DEX와 마켓 메이커를 통해 경쟁력 있는 가격과 낮은 네트워크 수수료를 제공하기 때문에 이더리움, 아비트럼, Optimism, BNB 체인, Polygon, 아발란체를 한 번의 간단한 방법으로 스왑할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h4>브릿지: 여러 네트워크 간 자산 이동</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio의 \"브릿지\" 기능으로 사용자는 [다양한 네트워크 전반에서 자산을 전송할 수 있습니다].(<a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/bridge-easily-move-tokens-across-chains/\">https://metamask.io/news/latest/bridge-easily-move-tokens-across-chains/</a>) 항공편 애그리게이터가 가장 저렴하거나 가장 빠른 항공편을 찾는 데 도움을 주는 것과 마찬가지로, 브리지 기능은 다른 네트워크로 가는 가장 저렴하거나 가장 빠른 경로를 찾도록 도와주어 좋은 거래를 할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h4>스테이크: 네트워크 보안</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio의 \"스테이크\" 기능을 사용하여 사용자는 로켓풀과 리도의 [유동성 스테이킹 공급자에 바로 액세스 할 수 있습니다].(<a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/stake-secure-the-network/\">https://metamask.io/news/latest/stake-secure-the-network/</a>) ETH를 간편하게 스테이킹하고 인출할 수 있으며 이더리움 네트워크 보안에 기여한 대가로 적립한 보상을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em><strong>MetaMask Portfolio: 웹3의 모든 것을 추적하고 관리하세요</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>MetaMask Portfolio는 웹3.0의 필요를 충족하고 사용자가 모든 것을 제어할 수 있는 사용자 친화적 종합 플랫폼입니다. 대시보드를 통해 매수, 스왑, 브리지, 스테이크 등 모든 활동을 할 수 있습니다. MetaMask Portfolio는 의미 있는 업데이트를 통해 지속적으로 디앱을 개선하고 발전시키기 위해 노력하고 있습니다. <a href=\"https://metamask.io/portfolio/?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">여기</a>를 클릭하여 MetaMask Portfolio와 그 기능을 자세히 알아보세요.</em></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":"MetaMask Portfolio는 암호화폐 및 NFT 포트폴리오를 추적하고 관리할 수 있는 디앱(DApp)입니다.","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false},"news_bg":{"file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3hGSTCAVrdhSMmLJHSHOWT/94799532e03716ceb32ad39268bef4b0/news-detail-bg.png"}},"news_dark_bg":{"file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/2StKLJf0XE38EyT9GlzQuO/ed29f2ebdc6b99f7ff32175a192133c3/news-detail-dark-bg.png"}},"hubspot":{"contentful_id":"5VZVKtbcRMzaaP77nsz3Fs","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulHubSpotForm"},"title":"Receive our Newsletter","description":null,"portalId":"4795067","formId":"fbfea1e4-e214-4ab2-a98b-964f9a81695a","campaignId":null,"displayTitle":true,"width":null,"customClass":"newsletterOnNewsDetail","customId":null},"latest":{"internal":{"type":"ContentfulLayoutModuleContainer"},"contentful_id":"nO1tqQRjoUDUJfdg2B651","node_locale":"ko","eyebrow":null,"headline":"최신 스토리 계속 읽기","description":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>개발자, 보안 뉴스 등</p>"}},"modules":[{"node_locale":"ko","contentful_id":"6iOGB8Fiab9ilS0jfZ8N5I","fontSize":null,"ctaLink":"/news/","displayText":"모든 게시물","displayTextTreatment":null,"newTab":false,"buttonDisplay":false,"buttonGradient":false,"buttonSecondary":false,"hideButtonIcon":null,"eventLabel":null,"eventCategory":null,"socialLink":null,"showCaretRight":null,"buttonCaretDown":null,"launchDarklyFlag":null,"customClassName":null,"internal":{"type":"ContentfulCta"},"hubSpotForm":null,"embedHTML":null,"downloadBrowsers":null,"mobileCta":null,"alternativeCta":null},{"contentful_id":"1B0wZMveBTSiMJZWu4uunI","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulModuleContainer"},"title":"News > Latest Stories (3 items)","description":null,"numberOfItem":3,"columns":3,"columnType":null,"columnsOnTablet":null,"centerOnTablet":null,"columnsOnMobile":1,"centerOnMobile":null,"contentAlignment":"left","splitModules":false,"displayTitle":false,"isLiquiditySection":false,"isTrustBar":null,"gridModulesGap":"12px","loadMoreMode":null,"loadMoreCta":null,"carouselMode":null,"hasRegionSelector":null,"regionSelectorHeadline":null,"regionSelectorPopupTitle":null,"regionSelectorPopupText":null,"regionListKey":null,"extraData":null,"modules":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}]}],"cta":null,"backgroundColor":"default","displayHeadline":true,"headlineAlignCenter":true,"contentAlignCenter":false,"headlineMarginTop0":null,"paddingTop":"40px","sectionPadding":null,"noPaddingTop":null,"noPaddingBottom":false,"modulesMargin":null,"isTab":false,"moduleId":null,"customClass":"storiesOnNewsDetail","sideImage":null,"backgroundSize":"cover","backgroundImage":null},"latestStories":{"nodes":[{"contentful_id":"3AVmlYVWKvlYZuzwT1UmEY","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"Introducing MetaMask Card pilot launch","slug":"introducing-metamask-card-upgrade-your-crypto-spending","subtitle":"MetaMask Card lets you spend crypto anywhere Mastercard is accepted. ","image":{"title":"MetaMask Card pilot launch ","description":"MetaMask Card pilot launch continues in the EU, UK, México, Colombia, and Brazil. ","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/1AqNjwlo0PRAS7UGJAoJYG/00abfdc80bbb28535e40e357d003b19e/Introducing-MetaMask-Card-Feature-v3__1_.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"December 11, 2024","authors":[{"name":"MetaMask","createProfilePage":null,"profileUrl":"metamask"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>MetaMask, Mastercard, and Baanx (Crypto Life) have launched MetaMask Card pilot, letting you make everyday purchases with your crypto anywhere Mastercard is accepted. <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/card\">MetaMask Card</a> functions like a crypto debit card, so you can spend directly from your MetaMask wallet.</p>\n<p>MetaMask Card pilot is currently available in the EU, UK, Brazil, Mexico, and Colombia. To get started, head to <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/card\">MetaMask Portfolio</a> and click on the <strong>Card</strong> tab. Eligible users will be redirected to the Crypto Life platform to set up their account and card.</p>\n<p>“MetaMask Card pilot gives people more freedom to spend crypto,” says Lorenzo Santos, Senior Product Manager at Consensys. “MetaMask Card represents a major step to removing the friction that has traditionally existed between the blockchain and real-world commerce. This is a paradigm shift that offers the best of both worlds.”</p>\n<p>Chief Commercial Officer at Baanx, Simon Jones shares, \"we are so delighted to partner with web3’s leading wallet, MetaMask, to power the financial revolution by enabling users to be their own bank.”</p>\n<h3>Accelerating crypto adoption by removing barriers to spending</h3>\n<p>In the past, off-ramping crypto to cash was clunky, and required many steps. This tedious process hindered mainstream adoption of crypto as a practical, real-world payment method. MetaMask Card removes the need to transfer your funds to a centralized exchange or a bank in order to spend your crypto. This not only paves the way for increased adoption, it also aligns with the MetaMask vision of empowering people with self-custody.</p>\n<p>Most traditional crypto cards operate similarly to prepaid cards, where you need to transfer funds to a third party before spending them. MetaMask Card is because it functions like a debit card. This means card holders can directly use the crypto in their MetaMask wallet for everyday purchases, and maintain control over their funds until the exact moment of payment. MetaMask Card utilizes Mastercard's global merchant network, combined with the security of MetaMask and the efficiency of <a href=\"https://linea.build/\">Linea</a> secured by the Ethereum network. This trio brings a swift, cost-effective, and secure spending experience, whether online or for in store purchases.</p>\n<h3>Global expansion of MetaMask Card</h3>\n<p>Get your MetaMask Card today, and begin using it immediately via digital wallet integrations with Apple Pay or Google Pay. Note: Eligible currencies include USDC, USDT, and WETH on Linea network. If you're outside of the EU, UK, Brazil, Mexico, and Colombia — you're not forgotten. MetaMask Card pilot is rolling out globally over the coming months. Join <a href=\"https://consensys-software.typeform.com/to/jj3MGjae\">our waitlist</a> to stay in the loop, and find out when MetaMask Card will be available where you are.</p>\n<p><strong>Need extra help? We got you. Check out our <a href=\"https://support.metamask.io/metamask-portfolio/card/getting-started/\">MetaMask Card Support Guide</a> for more details.</strong></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":"Introducing MetaMask Card: Upgrade Your Crypto Spending","metaDescription":"MetaMask Card is a crypto card that allows you to spend crypto anywhere Mastercard is accepted. MetaMask Card functions like a crypto debit card.","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false},{"contentful_id":"2VNhzxKzOPh5LW6odw2hAG","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"Simplifying crypto transactions with Banxa","slug":"simplifying-crypto-transactions-with-banxa","subtitle":"Meet the builders who are transforming web3, in our More With MetaMask Partner Series. ","image":{"title":"More with MetaMask Partner Series Banxa ","description":"More with MetaMask Partner Series Banxa ","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=960&h=541&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=1920&h=1081&q=80&fm=webp 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=3840&h=2162&q=80&fm=webp 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=1920&h=1081&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=960&h=541&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=1920&h=1081&q=80&fm=png 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3wvjFfE7M4SSkiwZ6arTCa/b69613e4a9793ea75400f00275443728/24-12-4_MwM_Blog-Banxa.png?w=3840&h=2162&q=80&fm=png 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1081}},"publishDate":"December 5, 2024","authors":[{"name":"Tom Chalmers","createProfilePage":false,"profileUrl":"tom-chalmers"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>MetaMask is the gateway to the decentralized web, enabling you to do more. Users can connect to any dapp, on any network, from any device. From DeFi to DeSci, gaming to NFTs, and beyond: MetaMask is passionate about the web3 community. Our More With MetaMask Partner Series shines a light on builders who are innovating across the ecosystem. Next up, Banxa.</strong></p>\n<p>Navigating crypto used to be a complicated process, but no longer. At <a href=\"https://banxa.com/product-on-off-ramps/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-8795857-afbf08\">Banxa</a>, our mission is to simplify crypto onboarding. As a leading crypto on-ramp and off-ramp solution integrated with <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/buy?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-8775817-afbf08\">MetaMask</a>, we exchange your fiat money for cryptocurrency and vice versa.</p>\n<p>Without Banxa, crypto wallets like MetaMask would need numerous integrations, partnerships, and licenses to help their users buy and sell crypto. This process is time-consuming, resource intensive, and involves additional risks and regulatory responsibilities. Banxa handles all of these logistics, so MetaMask can focus on what matters – building web3 products that users love.</p>\n<h2>Configurable crypto journeys</h2>\n<p><strong>Tailored experiences:</strong> MetaMask’s configurability ensures the best experience for every customer, whether you are a new or returning user.</p>\n<p><strong>Streamlined onboarding:</strong> For new users, Banxa minimizes the steps needed to buy and sell crypto.</p>\n<p><strong>Effortless transactions:</strong> Returning users can complete purchases in just one click without leaving MetaMask app, thanks to prior verification.</p>\n<h2>Worldwide user reach</h2>\n<p>MetaMask's commitment to accessibility works in tandem with Banxa's vision of global web3 onboarding. Leveraging MetaMask's user-friendly interface and extensive features, Banxa reaches a wider audience, providing an easy gateway to the world of cryptocurrencies. MetaMask’s configurability also improves our ability to deliver superior experiences to Banxa users.</p>\n<h2>Powerful web3 APIs</h2>\n<p>MetaMask provides a robust suite of web3 APIs that serve as a gold standard for product integration. These APIs offer a seamless and standardized approach for Banxa to connect its services with MetaMask, enabling smooth user experiences and efficient transactions.</p>\n<p>By integrating Banxa's smooth on-ramp and off-ramp solutions with MetaMask, we've made it easier than ever for users to navigate the decentralized web. The complexity of crypto is no longer a barrier to entry.</p>\n<p><strong>Experience the ease of buying crypto with <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/buy?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-8775817-afbf08\">MetaMask</a> via Banxa today.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Looking for more help? We got you. Learn <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/how-to-buy-crypto/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-8785843-afbf08\">how to buy crypto</a> on MetaMask.</strong></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"me